Title: What is ChatGPT? 
 
ChatGPT is an advanced language model developed by OpenAI. It uses deep learning to generate human-like text based on input. It can answer questions, assist with content creation, translate languages, and more. 
 
Key Features: 
-	Natural conversation 
-	Context-aware responses 
-	Multi-language support 
-	Ideal for chatbots and assistants 
